{"about_the_game":"Dive into a realm where the art of subterfuge meets the cutting edge of technology. As the ultimate covert operative, your mission extends beyond mere infiltration \u2013 assassinate high-profile targets, breach impregnable security zones, and liberate priceless treasures from the clutches of the elite.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700020/extras/Augment_Your_Arsenal.png?t=1729022749\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700020/extras/Augment_2.gif?t=1729022749\" /><br>Command a suite of over 32 augmentations, shaping your body into the epitome of stealth and combat prowess. Grappling hooks, silent footfalls, and combat maneuvers await strategic deployment, each choice defining your destiny.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700020/extras/Gear_Up_For_Stealth.png?t=1729022749\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700020/extras/Stealth_3.gif?t=1729022749\" /><br>Elevate your arsenal with 7 distinctive swords and 8 crossbows, each boasting unique abilities. From explosive parry swords to crossbows seeking out enemies, tailor your loadout for any shadowy challenge.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700020/extras/Bolts_For_Every_Occasion.png?t=1729022749\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700020/extras/Bolts_3.gif?t=1729022749\" /><br>Adapt to ever-changing landscapes with an arsenal of diverse bolt types, 8 attuned to your surroundings. Paralyze foes, create distractions, or vanish in a smokescreen.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700020/extras/Dynamic_Environments.png?t=1729022749\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700020/extras/Dynamic_3.gif?t=1729022749\" /><br>Embark on missions across diverse landscapes, from opulent mansions to murky slums, uncovering secrets within the underworld. Confront soulforged drones, slumdog gangs, mansion guards, and the enigmatic Luminaris Order.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700020/extras/Choose_Your_Approach.png?t=1729022749\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700020/extras/Approach_3.gif?t=1729022749\" /><br>Immerse yourself in an immersive sim, offering multiple paths. Leverage jump augments for towering heights or use brute strength to kick down doors. Skip dangerous paths with augments. Use imagination to solve problems and dominate your enemies.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700020/extras/Earnings_and_Investments.png?t=1729022749\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700020/extras/Earnings_3.gif?t=1729022749\" /><br>Successfully navigate each mission, accrue credits for personal enhancements. Unlock augmentations, purchase cutting-edge weapons, and secure consumables to bolster your chances. Are you prepared to become the ultimate agent of shadows?<br><br>The intricate web of intrigue awaits. Will you immerse yourself in its shadows?","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2700020?t=1729022749","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700020/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1729022749","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2700020/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1729022749","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/st